<cb:div type="taisho-notes">
<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0649004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0649004">之二＝中【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0649005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0649005">〔名〕－【三】，名＝多【宮】</note>
